1. **Strašna** oluja je pogodila grad. (A **terrible** storm hit the city.)
2. Ova igra je **strašno** zarazna. (This game is **terribly** addictive.)
3. Kada sam videla tu nesreću, osetila sam **strašan** strah. (When I saw that accident, I felt a **terrible** fear.)
4. *Strašan* je taj novi film koji svi hvale. (*Terrible* is that new movie that everyone praises.)
5. On je **strašno** dobar u matematici. (He is **terrifically** good at math.)
6. Ova situacija je **strašna** za sve nas. (This situation is **terrible** for all of us.)
7. **Strašni** zvuci su dopirali iz šume. (**Eerie** sounds were coming from the forest.)
8. Kada sam videla tu sliku, osetila sam **strašnu** tugu. (When I saw that picture, I felt a **terrible** sadness.)
9. Ona je **strašno** ljuta na mene. (She is **terribly** angry with me.)
10. *Strašan* je taj čovek, nikad ne znaš šta će da uradi. (*Terrible* is that man, you never know what he'll do.)